text: Ashlee Nicole DeLoach (or Nikki; born September 9, 1979) is an American actress and former singer. She was on The Mickey Mouse Club in the 1990s. She also played Lily in the 2008 version of An American Carol. DeLoach was born in Waycross, Georgia. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:1979 births Category:Living people
